name: The monoliths #7
description:
The seventh piece in the monoliths series was sent to @tormential
 on the 20th of September 2021 in the second year of the pandemic. It occurred to me as we pass 333K objkts that there will soon be an objkt that is closer to 500K than it is to 250k. Three-eighths of a million objkts. I am thinking this series will still be going at that point.
